      • getDevicePermissions

        public Map<String,List<DevicePermission>> getDevicePermissions()
        The method to retrieve the assigned device permissions of a user. The map contains a series of keys of device ids, and the values are a list of permissions of different type.
        Returns:
        a map of device permissions for this user or null if the user has no permissions

      • setDevicePermissions

        public void setDevicePermissions(Map<String,List<DevicePermission>> devicePermissions)
        The method to set device permissions to a user. It allows to set more than one type of device permissions for more than one device at once by employing a map of device ids and a list of permissions. Will overwrite all existing permissions in this User instance.
        Parameters:
        devicePermissions - the new permissions for this user.
